iti104:2.1:
“Monks, those monks who are consummate in virtue, consummate in concentration,
consummate in discernment, consummate in release, consummate in the knowledge & vision of release;
who exhort, demonstrate, instruct, urge, rouse & encourage;
who are competent rightly to point out the true Dhamma:
seeing them, I tell you, accomplishes a great deal;
